lution in the normalization of the dust-to-gas ratio DGR vs.\nmetallicity relation from $z\\sim0$ to $z\\sim2$. This result is consistent with\nsome semi-analytic models and cosmological simulations describing the evolution\nof dust in galaxies. Tracing the actual form of the DGR vs. metallicity\nrelation at high redshift now requires combined measurements of dust, gas, and\nmetallicity over a significantly wider range in metallicity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2020 18:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2020 17:14:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
