s of PICO, our filter will be able to characterize sources down to a\nminimum polarization intensity of, respectively, 125 pK and 14 pK. Adopting a\n$\\Pi=0.02$ polarization degree, these values correspond to 169 mJy and 288 mJy\nintensities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2020 10:38:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2021 08:58:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-31"}
